<br />
<br />stuff:
<br />      lda $2002
<br />      and #%01000000
<br />      bne lada
<br />      inc scrollx
<br />      lda scrollx
<br />      sta $2005
<br />      rts
<br />
<br />lada:
<br />     rts
<br />
<br />But that's what I used in my NMI routine, to get my sprite collide with color demo. Wow, I'm even more proud of that demo than I thought. I could really manipulate that effect to my own good. Okay, but I think I'm getting close, I just need a little more help here. Thank you, this is very helpful! <img src="./images/smilies/icon_smile.gif" alt=":)" title="Smile" /></div>

